expression.expression:
CASE
  WHEN (AMOUNT > 10000)
    THEN 'Flagged'
  ELSE 'Not Flagged'
END

CASE
  WHEN (month(to_date(ORDER_DATE)) IN (12, 1, 2))
    THEN 'Winter'
  WHEN (month(to_date(ORDER_DATE)) IN (3, 4, 5))
    THEN 'Spring'
  WHEN (month(to_date(ORDER_DATE)) IN (6, 7, 8))
    THEN 'Summer'
  ELSE 'Fall'
END
